title: Exhaust Sound: MagnaFlow Cat-Back Exhaust System on a BMW M3 (F8x)
description: Hear what it sounds like when you equip your M3 with a premium MagnaFlow Cat-Back Exhaust.

asset.title: MagnaFlow BMW M3 (F8x) Cat-Back Exhaust System - Sound Clip
asset.description: Made in the USA and engineered to last, MagnaFlow performance exhausts system deliver the sound you want and the power you need. MagnaFlow is the right exhaust for your daily driver, track star or custom show stopper BMW. With power support options, black or polished finished and even systems to satisfy your ears desire for more or less sound, you can choose the MagnaFlow system that no only fits your car but satisfies your personal tastes and needs.
